<br>
Of course, true, while reading that thread, there is no debate according to the wording of the EULA, but dang, who needs EQW to do anything nefarious? There's pleanty of programs out there that do such things as keyboard sniffing (reading direct keystrokes) to allow you to access the program while in the background. Add a little voice module to that, and viola, interaction with a program in the background! You can even have EQ running as normal <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
And, Mr Showeq, &quot;gameplay&quot; is an interaction between the person and the game itself, as well as how the game plays. Some aspects of the game are intentionally supposed to be 'difficult' or 'obtuse' to some. By knowing what's going on as it happens alters gameplay just because you know something you couldn't have from your avatar in game.<br>
<br>
Of course, printing out maps, keeping a book of tradeskill recipes, looking up spoiler info also alters gameplay, so perhaps we aught to shut that down too as '3rd party software' that destroys EQ's original intent <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
So long as you don't cheat, I think VI is apt to just blow it off as not worth the effort to track you down to ban you. Remember, Ban = loss of money. If you cheat, though, it's a risk of &quot;Ban 1 Person&quot; vs &quot;Lose lots of people because cheaters take it all&quot;. The equation isn't hard to figure out <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ninjacorp.com/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7714.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=7714.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=7714.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7714.topic&index=21><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.threadControl?topicID=7714.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7714.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification o